sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Voyageur
    participant M as Mobile App
    participant API as NestJS API
    participant EC as EnquiriesController
    participant ES as EnquiriesService
    participant P as PrismaService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>M: Soumettre une demande de voyage
    M->>API: POST /enquiries
    API->>EC: createEnquiry(dto)
    EC->>ES: createEnquiry(dto)
    ES->>P: enquiry.create(...)
    P->>DB: INSERT INTO enquiries
    DB-->>P: Saved row
    P-->>ES: EnquiryEntity
    ES-->>EC: EnquiryEntity
    EC-->>API: 201 Created
    API-->>M: Enquiry response
    M-->>U: Afficher la confirmation
